http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/One-held-for-online-betting/article13988510.ece

The Central Crime Branch sleuths have busted a cricket betting racket and arrested a 35-year-old man for offering bets online for Sydney Thunder v Perth Scorchers played at Sydney showground stadium on Thursday.Based on a tip-off the police raided the house situated in Palace Guttahalli and arrested Kishore Nandalal Ghora. The police recovered Rs 1.02 lakh, three mobile phones and other equipment from him.